headline: AutoZone to Release Third Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings May 27, 2025
summary: MEMPHIS, Tenn., April 28, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- AutoZone, Inc. (NYSE: AZO), the leading retailer and distributor of automotive replacement parts and accessories in the Americas, will release results for its third quarter ended Saturday, May 10, 2025, before market open on Tuesday, May 27, 2025. Additionally, the Company will host a one-hour conference call on Tuesday, May 27, 2025, beginning at 10:00 a.m. (ET), to discuss the results of the quarter.
